period_or_week: Carcass Survey Detail for Lower American River Fall Chinook Females Fresh All Survey Years

SacPAS has standardized values across the carcass survey detail datasets in order to present them jointly in this query. There are differences in data and covariates recorded for each survey. For the original datasets and more information about the carcass surveys, please refer to the information and files published on CalFish.

Lower American River Fall Run Chinook Salmon Escapement Survey, CalFish, https://www.calfish.org/ProgramsData/ConservationandManagement/CentralValleyMonitoring/SacramentoValleyTributaryMonitoring/LowerAmericanRiver.aspx
Dataset disclaimer: Please note data presented here are preliminary and subject to revision.
Survey section river miles are documented in the annual reports found on CalFish.
Dataset reports sample types collected individually as head_id, scale_id, tissue_id, and otolith_id.
Citation: Columbia Basin Research, University of Washington. (2025). SacPAS Carcass Survey Detail. Available from cbr.washington.edu/sacramento/data/query_carcass_detail.html.
